At the moment, we are still making a web interface that will be crucial for companies to send shipments, fill in the data about them on the website, so they will create points on the map.
We are then able to invoice them every month.
Are you currently working on the project full-time?
It's getting used to it, but we normally have it at work to feed and develop the project.
There is no strong multinational investor behind us, we are two guys, one of whom had a brilliant idea and the other jumped into it with other stimuli and ideas.
Now we are looking for an investor strong enough to manage with us to manage not the Czech market, but who should go with us to the global product with us and become another huge player in the market like AirBnB and Uber.
